HEADWORD: bear jam
<hw>bear jam</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A <isa>traffic
jam</isa> caused by tourists stopping to look at bears near the road; --
a phenomenon once common in Yellowstone Park, Wyoming.</def>
<mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
